  "important_notes": [
    "JMX name pattern: 'debezium.<connectorType>:type=connector-metrics,context=<snapshot|streaming>,server=<name>'",
    "Metrics.register() registers 'this' as MBean — concrete classes must be MXBean implementations",
    "PipelineMetrics delegates all event counting to CommonEventMeter, queue metrics to ChangeEventQueueMetrics",
    "DefaultSnapshotChangeEventSourceMetrics uses context='snapshot'; DefaultStreamingChangeEventSourceMetrics uses 'streaming'",
    "DefaultStreamingChangeEventSourceMetrics.onEvent conditionally invokes activityMonitoringMeter based on isAdvancedMetricsEnabled()",
    "CapturedTablesSupplier is a @FunctionalInterface injected into DefaultStreamingChangeEventSourceMetrics and passed to StreamingMeter",
    "All concrete metrics classes are @ThreadSafe"
  ],

